column5: Where does Little Dogtooth floe into Dogtooth lake?

There is a small lake(Mud Lake) that flows into Dogtooth Lake at the north east tip of Dogtooth Lake. Just a short liftover of some rapids.Travel east through Mud Lake and there is a portage into Hawk Lake.
Mud Lake = Little Dogtooth Same body of water two different names. Hawk to Little Dogtooth (Mud Lake) to Dogtooth.b-
